a\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>Metadata for a selection of performance indicators from the World Bank GovTech Maturity Index. 2025. Source: <a href=\"https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/search/dataset/0037889/govtech-datasetCloud\">https://datacatalog.worldbank.org/search/dataset/0037889/govtech-datasetCloud</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"shared-cloud-platform\">Shared cloud platform<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#shared-cloud-platform\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Chapter</td>\n<td>GovTech Maturity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>govtech-cloud-1</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Is there a shared cloud platform available for all government entities?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown/n.a;1=No;2=Only cloud strategy/policy (no platform yet);3=Yes (platform in use)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"cloud-platform-type\">Cloud platform type<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#cloud-platform-type\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Chapter</td>\n<td>GovTech Maturity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>govtech-cloud-1.4</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Type of cloud platform established</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unkown/n.a.;1=Public (Commercial);2=Private (Government);3=Hybrid</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Type of cloud &gt; Public: Commercial operators; outside/in country; Private: Operated by government entities; on-premise, 3= Hybrid (combination of public \\&amp; private)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"hosting-policy\">Hosting policy<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#hosting-policy\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Chapter</td>\n<td>GovTech Maturity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>govtech-cloud-1.6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Government Cloud data hosting policy?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unknown/n.a;1=No policy / Unkown/n.a.;2=Keeping data inside the country;3=Keeping data outside the country;4=Hybrid (inside + outside)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"service-provided\">Service provided<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#service-provided\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Chapter</td>\n<td>GovTech Maturity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>govtech-cloud-1.7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Cloud services provided</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unkown/n.a.;1=SaaS;2=PaaS;3=IaaS;4=XaaS</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td>Cloud services &gt; SaaS: Software as a Service; PaaS: Platform as a Service; IaaS: Infrastructure as a Service; XaaS: Anything as a Service</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"single-shared-platform\">Single shared platform<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#single-shared-platform\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Chapter</td>\n<td>GovTech Maturity</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Variable Id</td>\n<td>govtech-cloud-1.8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Definition</td>\n<td>Is there one shared Government Cloud platform or several?</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Format</td>\n<td>0=Unkown/n.a.;1=Several cloud platforms (Central/Local levels);2=One shared cloud platform</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Other Metadata</td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"transparency\">Transparency<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#transparency\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h3>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Field</th>\n<th>Value</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<